# Tomb Raider Launch Directory

When launching `trl.exe`, always use `A:\SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\Tomb Raider Legend` as the working directory.

Do not launch `trl.exe` from the repo root or any other folder.

If using `Start-Process`, pass the game directory as `-WorkingDirectory` or run the command from that directory.

Reason: the game resolves `bigfile.*` archives relative to its current working directory, and the wrong launch directory causes `Failed to open BIGFILE.000`.
